<node CREATED="1576216631430" ID="ID_549613810" MODIFIED="1576216631430" TEXT="The name Atom applies to a pair of related Web standards.The Atom Syndication Format is an XML language used for web feeds while the Atom Publishing Protocol (AtomPub or APP) is a simple HTTP-based protocol for creating and updating web resources.. Web feeds allow software programs to check for updates published on a website. To provide a web feed the site owner may use specialized software " />
