<node CREATED="1576216631430" ID="ID_1720442763" MODIFIED="1576216631430" TEXT="As a publishing protocol AtomPub provides a standard mechanism for creating and editing resources and resolving any arising conflicts. AtomPub extends the Atom format with a number of new publishing-related elements; at the same time it specifies the HTTP idioms that can be used to manipulate published content." />
