<node CREATED="1576216631435" ID="ID_646392378" MODIFIED="1576216631435" TEXT="EBS Snapshot EBS provides the ability to create snapshots (backups) of any EBS volume and write a copy of the data in the volume to Amazon S3 where it is stored redundantly in multiple Availability Zones Snapshots can be used to create new volumes increase the size of the volumes or replicate data across Availability Zones Snapshots&#226;&#8364;&#166;" />
</node>
