<node CREATED="1576216631435" ID="ID_1995016137" MODIFIED="1576216631435" TEXT="EBS volumes can be backed up by creating a snapshot of the volume which is stored in Amazon S3. EBS volumes can be created from a snapshot can be attached to an another instance within the same region; EBS volumes are created in a specific Availability Zone and can then be attached to any instances in that same Availability Zone." />
</node>
